=Show API Version=
This operation is used to view the API version information

==Request==

{| class="wikitable"
|-
| Method || GET
|-
|Request URI || 
* XML format
 /api_version.xml
* JSON format
 /api_version.json
|}

'''Request Body'''
:None

==Response==

{| class = "wikitable"
|-
|Response Body(XML format) ||
 <?xml version="1.0"
  encoding="UTF-8"
  standalone="yes"?>
  <api_version version="{version}"/>

|-
|Response Body(JSON format) ||
 {
  "api_version": {
          "version": "{version}"
         }
 }
|}

'''Description of Response Elements'''
{| class = "wikitable"
|-
|Element || Description
|-
|version || API version.
Valid value: Vn.n where n is a
positive integer.
|}

